{"tid":1854253,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【再休息病死】其實我地係唔係要圍政總先肯封關？","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T11:44:39.000Z","uid":58351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3929d11b3a41576a54e9ca8f64f6753e5221f6","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"呢場疫症肯一早封關就已經解決咗八成<br />\n個政府仲係執迷不悟， 死都要奶習敗北<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋作為香港人係唔係應該要攞番六月嘅熱誠出嚟， 行出嚟爭取返一個自救嘅機會？<br />\n<br />\n唔係鼓勵大家送頭，<br />\n不過大家真係要好好思考下行動detail <br />\n<br />\n呢個政府只係會欺善怕惡，<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沉默只會被人當契弟</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6d3d7fe5d0f30eb97ec34299b216b007c41ffc4","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4636da670935ac9b39441f28d929873a11978e8","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"香港人已經開始畀人禁止入境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再唔反抗就大家一齊共享強國榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755c05f3e3f7d0003aa9d4fd69c8929af6305a7c","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5bf5adfe6dc653ff721ef03c2833deebc84a2544","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"64234470a8c85d4f36a0c0a65632cae302953d69","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ed34176952860249322d4dfa71b719eb8cac54d","tid":1854253,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"push"}]}